  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The table above shows the number of people who work in the Human Resources and Accounting departments of a company and the highest level of education they have completed. A person from one of these departments is to be chosen at random. If the person chosen works in the Human Resources department, what is the probability that the highest level of education the person completed is a master&rsquo;s degree?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<span class=\"math_expression \">\n            <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the fraction 2 over 15\"></span></span>\n"
